28 2.528 0 0 1 2.522-2.521A2.528 2.528 0 0 1 24 8.834a2.528 2.528 0 0 1-2.522 2.521h-2.522V8.834zM17.688 8.834a2.528 2.528 0 0 1-2.523 2.521 2.527 2.527 0 0 1-2.52-2.521V2.522A2.527 2.527 0 0 1 15.165 0a2.528 2.528 0 0 1 2.523 2.522v6.312zM15.165 18.956a2.528 2.528 0 0 1 2.523 2.522A2.528 2.528 0 0 1 15.165 24a2.527 2.527 0 0 1-2.52-2.522v-2.522h2.52zM15.165 17.688a2.527 2.527 0 0 1-2.52-2.523 2.526 2.526 0 0 1 2.52-2.52h6.313A2.527 2.527 0 0 1 24 15.165a2.528 2.528 0 0 1-2.522 2.523h-6.313z"></path></svg></a><a aria-label="YouTube" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/@livekit_io" class="text-fg2 hover:text-lk-500 transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5"><title>YouTube</title><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><main id="main-content" class="min-h-screen pb-20"><div class="px-6"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl mt-4 space-y-16 lg:mt-20"><section><div class="text-fg0 space-y-2 max-w-prose"><h1 class="z-20 tracking-tight text-pretty lg:text-5xl text-4xl font-light"><span>Brand<!-- --> </span><span style="opacity:1;color:#1fd5f9;filter:drop-shadow(0px 0px 8px #035c6d)">assets<!-- --> </span></h1><div class="lg:font-regular font-regular text-fg2 pt-2 lg:text-lg text-base"><div class="max-w-prose text-pretty">Our brand assets help you reference LiveKit consistently and clearly. You’re free to use them when talking about or representing LiveKit. For usage in combination with other brands or graphics, partnerships, advertising or promotional use, please contact<!-- --> <a href="mailto:marketing@livekit.io" class="text-fg0 hover:text-fgAccent1 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">marketing@livekit.io</a>.</div></div></div><div class="mt-8 w-fit"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/brand/brand-assets.zip" class="text-md border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg0 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 inline-block rounded-md border px-4 py-2 transition-colors">Download all assets</a></div></section><hr class="border-separator1 w-full"/><section><h2 class="text-fg0 mb-12 font-mono text-base font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Brand elements</h2><div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:gap-20 lg:px-0"><div class="flex flex-1 flex-col justify-between gap-10"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h3 class="text-fg0 text-lg font-semibold">Wordmark</h3><p class="text-base">LiveKit primary logo is the wordmark. It should be used in most cases to clearly represent LiveKit brand. When referring to our brand in writing, use LiveKit as the preferred form. Avoid using variations such as LIVEKIT, Livekit, or any other modifications.</p></div><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><img src="/brand/LK-wordmark.png" alt="LiveKit Logo" class="w-full object-contain"/></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs absolute top-2 right-2 z-10 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy SVG</button></div></div><div class="flex flex-1 flex-col justify-between gap-10"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h3 class="text-fg0 text-lg font-semibold">Symbol</h3><p class="text-base">The LiveKit symbol serves as a compact, recognizable representation of our brand. Designed for scalability, it maintains clarity in small spaces such as app icons, avatars, and other minimal layouts.</p></div><div class=""><div class="flex h-full w-full justify-end gap-3 rounded-lg"><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><img src="/brand/LK-colored.png" alt="LiveKit logo" class="h-full w-full rounded-lg object-contain"/></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs absolute top-2 right-2 z-10 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy SVG</button></div><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><img src="/brand/LK-negative.png" alt="LiveKit logo in negative" class="h-full w-full rounded-lg object-contain"/></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs transition-colors transitiovgcity absolute top-2 right-2 z-10 group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy SVG</button></div></div></div></div></div></section><hr class="border-separator1 w-full"/><section><div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:gap-20"><div class="top-24 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-10"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h3 class="text-fg0 text-lg font-semibold">Clearance</h3><p>The clear space around the wordmark ensures it remains distinct and unobstructed. This space is proportional to the logotype&#x27;s height, with x representing the minimum required clearance. Whenever possible, allow more than the specified minimum to enhance visibility and impact.</p></div></div><div class="flex-1"><div class="border-separator1 flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-lg border"><img src="/brand/LK-clearance.png" alt="LiveKit Logo"/></div></div></div></section><hr class="border-separator1 w-full"/><section><div class="flex flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:gap-20"><div class="top-24 flex flex-1 flex-col gap-10"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2"><h3 class="text-fg0 text-lg font-semibold">Colors</h3><p>LiveKit&#x27;s brand colors are minimal and intentional. In dark mode, cyan delivers a strong accent that highlights key actions. In light mode, blue carries the same strength and clarity ensuring balance across themes. A rich near-black grounds dark interfaces, while a bright near-white does the same in light mode, together they create clarity and contrast in realtime environments.</p></div></div><div class="flex-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-8"><div class="flex flex-col gap-3"><h4 class="text-fg3 font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Dark Mode</h4><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row"><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border h-32 w-full sm:h-24 bg-fgAccent1 text-bg1"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><div class="h-32 w-full sm:h-24"><div class="absolute flex w-full items-center justify-between pt-2 pr-2 pl-3"><span class="block w-24 font-mono text-sm">#1FD5F9</span><div class="flex-1"></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy hex</button></div></div></div></div><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border h-32 w-full sm:h-24 bg-bg1 text-fg0"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><div class="h-32 w-full sm:h-24"><div class="absolute flex w-full items-center justify-between pt-2 pr-2 pl-3"><span class="block w-24 font-mono text-sm">#070707</span><div class="flex-1"></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy hex</button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-3"><h4 class="text-fg3 font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Light Mode</h4><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row"><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border h-32 w-full sm:h-24 bg-blue-500 text-fg0"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><div class="h-32 w-full sm:h-24"><div class="absolute flex w-full items-center justify-between pt-2 pr-2 pl-3"><span class="block w-24 font-mono text-sm">#002CF2</span><div class="flex-1"></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy hex</button></div></div></div></div><div class="border-separator1 hover:border-separator2 group relative rounded-lg border h-32 w-full sm:h-24 bg-[#FDFDFC] text-bg1"><div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-end"><div class="h-32 w-full sm:h-24"><div class="absolute flex w-full items-center justify-between pt-2 pr-2 pl-3"><span class="block w-24 font-mono text-sm">#FDFDFC</span><div class="flex-1"></div><button type="button" class="border-separator1 bg-bg2 text-fg1 hover:bg-bg3 focus:bg-bg3 flex h-6 items-center rounded-md border px-2 text-xs transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 md:opacity-0">Copy hex</button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><hr class="border-separator1 w-full"/><section class="text-fg0 flex w-full flex-col gap-10"><div class="text-fg0 space-y-2 max-w-prose"><h2 class="z-20 tracking-tight text-pretty lg:text-4xl text-3xl font-light"><span>Ready<!-- --> </span><span>to<!-- --> </span><span style="opacity:1;color:#1fd5f9;filter:drop-shadow(0px 0px 8px #035c6d)">build?<!-- --> </span></h2><p class="lg:font-regular font-regular text-fg2 pt-2 lg:text-base text-sm"><span class="inline-block max-w-prose text-pretty">Start building a voice AI agent with a free account. Reach out to us if you&#x27;re interested in custom pricing.</span></p></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-8"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row"><div class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:w-auto lg:grid-cols-2"><a href="https://cloud.livekit.io" target="_self" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden rounded-md px-4 py-2 border" tabindex="0" style="border-color:rgba(31, 213, 249, 0);background-color:#1FD5F9;filter:drop-shadow(0px 0px 8px rgba(31, 213, 249, 0.25))"><div class="relative overflow-hidden text-sm font-semibold"><div class="invisible">Start building</div><span class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex w-full flex-col" style="transform:translateY(0%)"><div class="text-bg1 h-full w-full">Start building</div><div class="text-fg0 h-full w-full">Start building</div></span></div></a><a class="border-separator1 bg-bg1 text-fg1 hover:border-separator2 hover:text-fg0 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border px-4 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight transition-all duration-150 hover:bg-bg2" href="/contact-sales">Contact sales</a></div></div><p class="text-fg1 text-sm">No credit card required • 1,000 free agent session minutes monthly</p></div></section></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><div class="px-6"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl"><footer class="border-separator1 w-full border-t py-16"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 lg:flex-row"><div class="min-w-52 flex-1 space-y-6"><a aria-label="LiveKit homepage" href="/"><div class="inline-block"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" class="h-5 w-5"><path d="M14.4004 9.59961H9.59961V14.4004H14.4004V9.59961Z" fill="oklch(var(--lk-color-fgAccent1)"></path><path d="M19.2011 4.80078H14.4004V9.60153H19.2011V4.80078Z" fill="oklch(var(--lk-color-fgAccent1)"></path><path d="M19.2011 14.4004H14.4004V19.2011H19.2011V14.4004Z" fill="oklch(var(--lk-color-fgAccent1)"></path><path d="M24 0H19.19